<section class="page hv-about-page">
  {% render 'breadcrumbs', page: page %}
  <div class="panel hv-policy hv-about">
    <p class="hv-about__badge">Collector-run · NZ based</p>
    <h1>{{ page.title | default: 'About HoloVault' }}</h1>
    <p class="hv-about__lead">HoloVault is a small New Zealand Pokémon TCG singles store built for collectors who want clear listings, real stock, and cards packed with care.</p>

    <div class="hv-about__grid">
      <div class="hv-about__card">
        <h2>What we sell</h2>
        <p>Individual singles across English, Japanese, and Chinese sets — sourced with collectors in mind and listed with honest condition notes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hv-about__card">
        <h2>How we pack</h2>
        <p>Cards are sleeved, protected, and shipped in rigid mailers or boxes. Higher-value cards get extra protection.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hv-about__card">
        <h2>Why we are small</h2>
        <p>We are intentionally not a massive warehouse. Every listing should help you complete a set — not overwhelm you with noise.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Market pricing</h2>
    <p>Listings use Collectr market data where applicable, with prices updated regularly so you see fair, current values in NZD.</p>

    <div class="hv-about__cta">
      <a class="btn primary" href="{% if collections.pokemon %}{{ collections.pokemon.url }}{% else %}{{ routes.all_products_collection_url }}{% endif %}">Browse singles</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="/pages/contact">Contact us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About page",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
